        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><h3>How far in advance should I book?</h3></summary>
          <p>For weddings, we recommend booking 6-12 months in advance, especially for peak season (May-October). Corporate events and private parties can typically be booked 2-3 months ahead. Popular dates fill quickly, so earlier is always better!</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
