          <p>Yes! We have professional-grade outdoor sound systems and weatherproof equipment. We bring backup power sources, weather-protected DJ booths, and have experience with all types of outdoor venues across North Alabama.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><h3>Can I request specific songs and create a playlist?</h3></summary>
          <p>Absolutely! We provide online planning tools where you can create must-play lists, do-not-play lists, and preferred genres. We work with you to create the perfect soundtrack for your event. Our extensive music library spans all decades and genres.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><h3>Do you have backup equipment?</h3></summary>
          <p>Yes! We bring backup equipment to every single event - including backup DJ controller, microphones, cables, and power supplies. Your event entertainment is guaranteed to run smoothly with no interruptions.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
